  "template": "Look! {SUBJ} ____ {OBJ} {PLACE}.",
  "example": "Look! They are playing chess in the living room.",
  "explanation": "Use 'are' + verb-ing with 'you/we/they' for actions happening now. 'Look!' draws attention to the current action.",
